description: The stories of Lodoss by Ryo Mizuno are one of the greatest manga and anime success stories ever! And Chronicles of the Heroic Knight has all the action, humor, and adventure of the previous series! In this first issue we meet Spark, the young knight-in-training, who dreams of being a glorious hero in the wars of Lodoss. He serves and waits for the day that his name will appear on the list of knights, but never gets the call... until he meets the real heroes who will shape his destiny: Parn, the heroic Knight of Tessius, and Deedlit, the Elf beloved by Lodoss fans everywhere! You can't miss this exciting new series!
